      <div class="field-group"><label>Manning <span title="Operators per machine. Laser/punch CNC: 0.5–1. Brake: 1–2. Robotic cell: 0.25–0.5.">ℹ</span></label><input type="number" id="smf-manning" step="0.25" min="0" value="1"/></div>
