          <div class="field-group"><label>Time / Spot (s) <span title="Per spot weld including electrode approach. Typical: 2–4s pedestal, 1–2s robotic.">ℹ</span></label><input type="number" id="smf-sw-t" step="0.5" min="0" value="3"/></div>
